<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l15">daʒ Jr Jn durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>wıllıge<ex>n</ex></expan> dinſte <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
