</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_275" id="137r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
